  "title": "Relationship Manager / MNC Bank / High Basic + Paid Training Provided",
  "description": "<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Basic up to $4200 Plus allowance and Commission</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Banking working environment</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Entry level into the banks</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Fantastic Career Progression</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Description</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Highly motivated individuals to promote and acquire New to Bank and existing customers by cross-selling the value propositions of banking facilities such as credit cards, banking accounts, or fund transfer programs to various consumer segment</li>\n  <li>Engage &amp; build good relationships with customers, generate sales referrals &amp; deliver good client experience</li>\n  <li>Good follow-up skills and ensuring customers' applications and documentation are completed for processing timely</li>\n  <li>Requires to meet performance standards, business goals, and sales targets</li>\n  <li>Able to present effectively and communicate comfortably to customers face-to-face or through telemarketing activities</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Qualifications</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum Diploma qualifications</li>\n  <li>The candidate must be confident, meticulous, possess good interpersonal and follow-up skills</li>\n  <li>Candidate needs to have good communication &amp; customer service skills</li>\n  <li>Sales-oriented and self-motivated candidate to excel in sales targets and goals</li>\n  <li>A team player with the ability to multi-task &amp; thrive in a banking sales environment</li>\n  <li>Computer literate, proficient with use of MS Office &amp; Outlook</li>\n  <li>Candidates without sales experience may apply</li>\n</ul>\n<p>For faster response, please email your updated resume in MS Words format with the following details to <strong>steven@starrecruitment.com.sg</strong></p>\n<p>1) Last Drawn Salary<br>\n2) Expected Salary<br>\n3) Recent Photo<br>\n4) Reason(s) for Leaving<br>\n5) Availability Period<br>\n6) References</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Steven Chan<br>\nRegistration No: R1105423<br>\nEA License No: 08C5257</p>",
